<br />Has anybody done tests on either of the two following hypotheses to see which is correct or what is the right value of <em>n</em>? <ul><li>Waits for PPU A12 to be low for at least <em>n</em> straight cycles. </li><li>Ignores PPU A12 for at least <em>n</em> cycles after a rising edge. </li></ul></div>

